Package: rmdmux
Type: Package
Title: Export A Single RMD File As Beautiful PDF And As Fully Accessible HTML
Description: The 'rmdmux' package is an 'R' package, which extends the 'rmarkdown' package.
    With 'rmdmux' it is possible to export a single RMD file at the same time
    as a beautiful PDF report and as an HTML file, which fulfills the
    WAI requirements and is therefore fully accessible for assistive reading
    devices like screen readers.
Version: 1.0.0
